// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0773 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 9b2d683c-730a-5c31-8926-c50a964d7f28

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
